headline.print_headline: Stenson Battles Past Tenacious Blixt to Reach Semis
headline.main: Stenson Battles Past Tenacious Blixt to Reach Semis

lead_paragraph: The apprentice made the sorcerer fight all the way before top seed Henrik Stenson scrambled a two-hole victory over fellow Swede Jonas Blixt at the Volvo World Match Play Championship on Saturday.
